{"id":152252,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/ubuntu-11-10将用lightdm替代gdm/","date":"2011-05-14T13:30:32Z","modified":"2011-05-14T13:30:32Z","title":"Ubuntu 11.10将用LightDM替代GDM","content":"<p>去年社区曾有流言声称，Ubuntu考虑用LightDM取代GDM。但这一转变并没有在Ubuntu 11.04中发生。在刚刚举行的Ubuntu开发者峰会上，官方证实Ubuntu 11.10将用LightDM替代GDM。 LightDM是一个轻量级的显示管理器，其优势在于速度更快，无需运行完整个GNOME会话；支持多种欢迎界面；代码更简单，只有5000行代码，相比之下GDM有50000行代码。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14cd7a8f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=Ubuntu+11.10%E5%B0%86%E7%94%A8LightDM%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3GDM&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Flinux.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F13%2F0632210%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=Ubuntu+11.10%E5%B0%86%E7%94%A8LightDM%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3GDM&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Flinux.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F13%2F0632210%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091019677/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14cd7a8f/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091019677/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14cd7a8f/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Hp9WNBxmA28:g6oe61lsnZk:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Hp9WNBxmA28:g6oe61lsnZk:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=